findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function isWhitelisted() uses a loop to find an address and will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long whitelisted array.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to pause and unpause token transfer, change burn and fund fee, change fund address, and add or remove addresses in whitelist.
